comments: Payton II (GSW) briefly places his hand to McDaniels' (MIN) side during the drive, which he is able to move through.
Wiggins (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Payton II (GSW) legally contests McDaniels's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Conley (MIN) makes incidental contact with Thompson's (GSW) foot as he is defending Curry (GSW).
Curry (GSW) releases from Conley (MIN) prior to his gather as the body contact that occurs is marginal.
Conley (MIN) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Payton II (GSW) briefly places both hands to Edwards' (MIN) side during the play.
Curry (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position and incidental contact occurs as he defends Edwards (MIN) at the end of the drive.
Wiggins (GSW) swipes down and initiates contact with Gobert's (MIN) arm that affects his shot attempt near the basket.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in Conley's (MIN) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Wiggins (GSW) slightly extends his lower body in McDaniels' (MIN) path and makes contact with his body during the screen, which does not affect his ability to defend
Green (GSW) backtracks slightly into Edwards' (MIN) path and brushes his body during the screen, which is marginal.
The ball is last touched by Gobert (MIN) prior to it going out of bounds.
McDaniels (MIN) briefly grasps Curry's (GSW) arm as he runs around the screen, which is marginal and does not affect Curry's FOM.
Curry (GSW) pins the ball to his body and resumes his dribble on the play.
McDaniels (MIN) slightly extends his leg in Curry's (GSW) path and makes contact with his lower body during the drive, which he is able to move through.
Anderson (MIN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Green (GSW) brings his hands toward Anderson (MIN) and the contact that occurs as Green (GSW) releases from the screen is marginal.
Paul (GSW) slightly extends his lower body in McDaniels' (MIN) path and brushes his body as he sets the screen, which is marginal.
Play is stopped as the shot clock was not reset to 14 after Thompson's (GSW) shot attempt makes contact with the rim.
Gobert (MIN) initiates contact with Curry's (GSW) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) extends his arm in Payton II's (GSW) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Payton II (GSW) legally contests Edwards's (MIN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
McDaniels (MIN) brushes Curry's (GSW) off-arm during the driving shot attempt, which is marginal.
Wiggins (GSW) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN).
Curry (GSW) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and is firming up when he absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Anderson (MIN) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Paul (GSW) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN).
